flowchart LR
    Prev([Property Manager]) -- assigns priorities to --> Role([Maintenance Supervisor])
    Role --> F1[Triage Incoming Requests]
    Role --> F2[Assign Techs & Contractors]
    Role --> F3[Manage Preventive Maintenance Schedule]
    Role --> F4[Approve Job Completion]
    Role --> F5[Escalate SLA Breaches]
    Role -- assigns jobs to --> Next1([Maintenance Tech])
    Role -- assigns jobs to --> Next2([Contractor])
